Prove 3.31

  (p ⋁ q) ⋁ (p ⋁ r)
=    〈 Associativity of ⋁ 〉
  p ⋁ (q ⋁ p) ⋁ r
=    〈 Symmetry of ⋁ 〉
  p ⋁ (p ⋁ q) ⋁ r
=    〈 Associativity of ⋁ 〉
  (p ⋁ p) ⋁ (q ⋁ r)
=    〈 Idempotency of ⋁ 〉
  p ⋁ (q ⋁ r)  ╱╱

