Prove 3.32

  p ⋁ q ≡ p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 Distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ (q ≡ ¬q)
=    〈 (3.15) p ≡ ¬p ≡ false 〉
  p ⋁ false
=    〈 Identity of ⋁ 〉
  p  ╱╱

