Prove 3.36

  p ⋀ q
=    〈 golden rule 〉
  p ≡ q ≡ p ⋁ q
=    〈 Symmetry of ≡ 〉
  q ≡ p ≡ p ⋁ q
=    〈 Symmetry of ⋁ 〉
  q ≡ p ≡ q ⋁ p
=    〈 golden rule 〉
  q ⋀ p  ╱╱

