Prove 3.47a

  ¬(p ⋀ q)
=    〈 Golden rule 〉
  ¬(p ≡ q ≡ p ⋁ q)
=    〈 Distributivity of ¬ over ≡ 〉
  ¬p ≡ q ≡ p ⋁ q
=    〈 (3.32) with p, q ≔ q, p 〉
  ¬p ≡ p ⋁ ¬q
=    〈 (3.32) with p, q ≔ ¬p, q 〉
  ¬p ⋁ ¬q  ╱╱

------------------------------

Prove 3.47b

  ¬(p ⋁ q)
=    〈 Double negation, twice 〉
  ¬(¬¬p ⋁ ¬¬q)
=    〈 De Morgan, (3.47a) with p, q ≔ ¬p, ¬q 〉
  ¬¬(¬p ⋀ ¬q)
=    〈 Double negation 〉
  ¬p ⋀ ¬q  ╱╱
